<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Present Stock Price</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous">

</head>
<body>

<div class = "container">

    <h1 class="display-4">Present Stock Price({{stocks.0.name}})</h1>
    <p class="lead">시세 현황 테이블</p>

    <div class="jumbotron">
        <h1 class="display-4">{{stocks.0.presentPrice}}</h1>
        <p class="lead">{{stocks.0.name}}의 현재가</p>
        <hr class="my-4">
        <h2>
            <span>전일 대비 증감량</span>
            <span>{{stocks.0.diffFromPrevDay}}</span>
        </h2>
    </div>
    <img src="{{stocks.0.imgURL}}" alt="chart" width="100%" style="margin:20px 0 20px 0">
    <table class= "table" style="margin-bottom: 50px">
        <tr>
            <th>이름</th>
            <th>전일 대비 증감량</th>
            <th>시가</th>
            <th>고가</th>
            <th title = "인구 10만 명당">저가</th>
        </tr>
        {{#each stocks}}
            <tr>
                <td>{{name}} </td>
                <td>{{diffFromPrevDay}}</td>
                <td>{{marketPrice}}</td>
                <td>{{high}}</td>
                <td>{{low}}</td>
            </tr>
        {{/each}}
    </table>
</div>

</body>
</html>